snippet.title: Elon Musk Jason Momoa and other Celebrities APOLOGIZING for Defending Amber Heard | The HollyVibe
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Jason Momoa and other Celebrities APOLOGIZING for Defending Amber Heard | The HollyVibe

Many celebrities (including Elon Musk and Jason Momoa) defended Amber Heard initially when accusations of abuse made against Johnny Depp. However, more and more evidence has come out showing that Amber Heard is indeed lying. Now everyone has turned against Amber Heard and now supporting Johnny Depp. The #FireAmberHeard movement is going strong. The Johnny Depp Amber Heard legal battle is still at the forefront of celebrity news. 

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnny

Cheers!
